{"meta":{"templateId":"placetel-rag-voice-assistant-onedrive-groq"},"name":"Placetel AI – RAG Voice Assistant with OneDrive & Supabase (Groq)","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"7518195d-5da5-4890-b82b-6bd0ffd7b7c1","name":"Sticky Note","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-848,-704],"parameters":{"color":4,"width":712,"height":636,"content":"📚 LOAD DATA FLOW – Dokumenten-Indexierung\n\nZweck:\nLiest Dokumente aus OneDrive und speichert sie\nals Vektoren in einer Vektordatenbank. Muss bei\nneuen Dokumenten manuell ausgeführt werden oder\nläuft automatisch per Schedule Trigger.\n\nAblauf:\n1. Dokumente auflisten (HTTP Request → Microsoft Graph API)\n2. IDs extrahieren (Code Node)\n3. Jede Datei einzeln verarbeiten (Loop)\n4. Datei herunterladen (OneDrive Node)\n5. Text laden & Vektoren erstellen (Embeddings)\n6. Chunks dauerhaft speichern (Supabase)\n\n⚠️ Konfiguration erforderlich:\n- Ordnerpfad in Graph API URL anpassen\n  (Standard: /me/drive/root:/ORDNERNAME:/children)\n- Microsoft OneDrive OAuth2 Credential hinterlegen\n- OpenAI API Key für Embeddings hinterlegen\n- Supabase Credentials hinterlegen\n- Nur unterstützte Dateiformate verwenden (.txt)"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"e52923fa-4c16-4732-9724-169b2491e078","name":"Sticky Note1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-848,-64],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":1372,"height":876,"content":"### 📚 Load Data Flow"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c05d0019-8ae7-4de3-a692-04259ccc0c08","name":"Sticky Note2","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[528,-64],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":840,"height":876,"content":"### 🎯 2. Retriever Flow"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"b0217cc1-1126-4ba2-8f99-83a1255eb170","name":"Sticky Note3","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[528,-720],"parameters":{"color":4,"width":832,"height":656,"content":"🎯 RETRIEVER FLOW – Wissensabfrage via Webhook\n\nZweck:\nEmpfängt Fragen per Webhook, durchsucht semantisch \ndie Vektordatenbank und gibt eine strukturierte \nAntwort zurück – optimiert für telefonische \nSprachausgabe.\n\nAblauf:\n1. Frage per Webhook empfangen (POST)\n2. Semantische Suche in Vektordatenbank\n3. Antwort via LLM generieren (Groq)\n4. Antwort an den Aufrufer zurückgeben\n\n⚠️ Konfiguration erforderlich:\n- Webhook URL in aufrufendem System hinterlegen\n- Erwarteter Request Body: { \"chatInput\": \"...\" }\n- System Prompt an Use Case anpassen\n- Groq API Key hinterlegen\n- Supabase Credentials hinterlegen\n- Gleiches Embeddings Modell wie Load Flow verwenden!"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"31b6e7a2-d798-43c7-9f81-83ce7e589696","name":"Sticky Note4","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[144,-288],"parameters":{"width":384,"height":260,"content":"⚠️ WICHTIG – Embeddings Konsistenz\n\nDas Embeddings Modell muss in BEIDEN Flows \nidentisch sein:\n- Load Data Flow: OpenAI Embeddings – Indexierung\n- Retriever Flow: OpenAI Embeddings – Abfrage\n\nUnterschiedliche Modelle führen zu \nfehlerhaften Suchergebnissen!\n\nEmpfohlen: text-embedding-3-small"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"52562725-0f05-40a2-9815-acc132557bc6","name":"Täglich 02:00 Uhr – Auto-Reindex","type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","position":[-832,160],"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"triggerAtHour":2}]}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"bf6dccfc-2ca2-484a-b359-6e1dbfdb78cc","name":"Manueller Start – Reindex","type":"n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger","position":[-832,320],"parameters":{},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"6d0948ee-6663-4c42-9441-83d2a9b25338","name":"OneDrive – Dateien auflisten","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[-624,320],"parameters":{"url":"https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/me/drive/root:/DEIN_ORDNERNAME:/children","options":{},"sendQuery":true,"authentication":"predefinedCredentialType","queryParameters":{"parameters":[]},"nodeCredentialType":"microsoftOneDriveOAuth2Api"},"typeVersion":4.4},{"id":"1e11decf-b114-4258-8e2c-031349d3afbf","name":"Datei-IDs extrahieren","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-192,512],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const files = $input.first().json.value;\nreturn files\n  .filter(f => f.file) // nur Dateien, keine Unterordner\n  .map(f => ({ json: f }));"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"81d6b05e-4a57-4031-a7c1-9614d93f1295","name":"Loop – Jede Datei","type":"n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches","position":[-368,320],"parameters":{"options":{}},"typeVersion":3},{"id":"32e2d7d2-c3af-4d9b-8c72-2b62895a0309","name":"OneDrive – Datei herunterladen","type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOneDrive","position":[32,512],"parameters":{"fileId":"={{ $json.id }}","operation":"download"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"23ad81df-3511-4349-a939-3a3ca172745f","name":"Text Loader","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.documentDefaultDataLoader","position":[224,304],"parameters":{"loader":"textLoader","options":{},"dataType":"binary"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"bbe09324-901b-4eec-977d-4769f95f7b02","name":"OpenAI Embeddings – Indexierung","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.embeddingsOpenAi","position":[-80,304],"parameters":{"options":{}},"typeVersion":1.2},{"id":"6497a9a3-2490-4f97-ac84-a06bd0255445","name":"Supabase – Chunks speichern","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.vectorStoreSupabase","position":[32,48],"parameters":{"mode":"insert","options":{"queryName":"match_documents"},"tableName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"documents","cachedResultName":"documents"}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"b3f2c29a-4ac5-4446-a4ce-5006453794e3","name":"Placetel – Webhook Eingang","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","position":[576,80],"parameters":{"path":"rag-knowledge-webhook","options":{},"httpMethod":"POST","responseMode":"responseNode"},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"a84d2684-202f-4430-91be-1cfec7cd9b79","name":"OpenAI Embeddings – Abfrage","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.embeddingsOpenAi","position":[976,672],"parameters":{"options":{}},"typeVersion":1.2},{"id":"65639571-6f7c-48b3-a402-60a924bee80e","name":"Placetel – Antwort zurückgeben","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","position":[1168,80],"parameters":{"options":{},"respondWith":"allIncomingItems"},"typeVersion":1.5},{"id":"66bb040f-078e-4b1c-a58c-34844e946d5c","name":"Question and Answer Chain","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainRetrievalQa","position":[800,80],"parameters":{"text":"={{ $json.body.chatInput }}","options":{},"promptType":"define"},"typeVersion":1.7},{"id":"1683b862-59a3-4930-9c39-84b937409bf0","name":"Vector Store Retriever","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.retrieverVectorStore","position":[928,288],"parameters":{"topK":3},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"09957cf9-3cf6-484b-b5eb-8111650a0145","name":"Supabase Vector Store","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.vectorStoreSupabase","position":[784,496],"parameters":{"options":{"queryName":"match_documents"},"tableName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"documents","cachedResultName":"documents"}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"c57e79d8-360c-4fdb-b346-f0ee1aeac5ac","name":"Groq Chat Model","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGroq","position":[688,288],"parameters":{"model":"llama-3.1-8b-instant","options":{}},"typeVersion":1}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"connections":{"Text Loader":{"ai_document":[[{"node":"Supabase – Chunks speichern","type":"ai_document","index":0}]]},"Groq Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Question and Answer Chain","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Loop – Jede Datei":{"main":[[{"node":"Supabase – Chunks speichern","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Datei-IDs extrahieren","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Datei-IDs extrahieren":{"main":[[{"node":"OneDrive – Datei herunterladen","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Supabase Vector Store":{"ai_vectorStore":[[{"node":"Vector Store Retriever","type":"ai_vectorStore","index":0}]]},"Vector Store Retriever":{"ai_retriever":[[{"node":"Question and Answer Chain","type":"ai_retriever","index":0}]]},"Question and Answer Chain":{"main":[[{"node":"Placetel – Antwort zurückgeben","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Manueller Start – Reindex":{"main":[[{"node":"OneDrive – Dateien auflisten","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Placetel – Webhook Eingang":{"main":[[{"node":"Question and Answer Chain","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Embeddings – Abfrage":{"ai_embedding":[[{"node":"Supabase Vector Store","type":"ai_embedding","index":0}]]},"Supabase – Chunks speichern":{"main":[[]]},"OneDrive – Dateien auflisten":{"main":[[{"node":"Loop – Jede Datei","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OneDrive – Datei herunterladen":{"main":[[{"node":"Loop – Jede Datei","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Embeddings – Indexierung":{"ai_embedding":[[{"node":"Supabase – Chunks speichern","type":"ai_embedding","index":0}]]},"Täglich 02:00 Uhr – Auto-Reindex":{"main":[[{"node":"OneDrive – Dateien auflisten","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}